{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1d66d6acb0","title":"中央文革小组关于斗争潘梓年的电话指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4fe97e7c34","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":9,"articleId":"1d66d6acb0"}],"tags":[{"id":"18bf6a78fe","name":"大联合","type":"主题"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"a0d5508956","name":"清查五·一六","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"87dfa5c6ff","name":"中央文革"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d35bb7c228","type":"title","text":"中央文革小组关于斗争潘梓年的电话指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1d66d6acb0"},{"id":"d5fd1367bb","type":"paragraph","text":"斗潘梓年，你们联合起来斗，你们要商量好，把准备工作作好，定好时间，再来电话请示，把人带去。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1d66d6acb0"},{"id":"f5cc4278f6","type":"paragraph","text":"领导上说了，你们联合起来斗，大批判应当联合起来搞，不能单方面去斗。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1d66d6acb0"},{"id":"e7872be31c","type":"paragraph","text":"办事组李春俊传达 67.10.9  18：55","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1d66d6acb0"},{"id":"708b10062f","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十日上午10：00又来电话：","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1d66d6acb0"},{"id":"41b1bdbaac","type":"paragraph","text":"要联合起来斗，这是中央首长指示精神，不是我们随便说的。你们可以将这个精神告诉大批判指挥部一下，也可以向群众传达一下。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1d66d6acb0"},{"id":"e40032d982","type":"paragraph","text":"李春俊","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1d66d6acb0"}],"page":{"id":"633912404a","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1d66d6acb0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}